                                                  High-Risk Customers

                       BUSINESS QUESTION
Can you identify customers who have been with us for exactly 12 months or less AND have Month-to-Month contracts AND are paying above the overall average monthly
charge. These are high-risk customers we need to contact

                         QUERY
SELECT
    Customer_ID,
    Tenure_in_Months,
    Contract,
    Monthly_Charge
FROM telecom_customer
WHERE Tenure_in_Months <= 12
    AND Contract = 'Month-to-Month'
    AND Monthly_Charge > (
        SELECT AVG(Monthly_Charge)
        FROM telecom_customer
    );

                                      KEY FINDINGS
These are customers paying higher monthly charges without long-term commitment, which may increase the likelihood forearly churn.
                                
                                   RECOMMENDATION
Thare is a need to offer discounts or incentives to encourage Month-to-Month customers to move to longer-term plans and improve their early experience
